<item>
            <title>[LU-8932] define a new network driver for ptl4lnd</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8932</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Assign an ID to the new network driver ptl4lnd developped by Bull/Atos to support a Portals4 based LND for the BXI interconnect.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am going to post a patch for this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
